Beautiful home located in Highland Lakes a 55 plus active community.This home has a open floor plan with a bonus room needs some Tlc  and offers laminate flooring throughout the home which was installed in 2022 and also A/C that was installed in 2021.The master bedroom has an ensuite bathroom with granite counter tops and a garden tub and a separate shower.The community has a club house has an indoor heated pool and cooking classses when available you can fish play tennis and pickle ball so much to do in this gated community you will not be bored residing here.
